WEBVTT

00:00:00.266 --> 00:00:03.236
Article 8 concerns routine counseling between Supervisors

00:00:03.303 --> 00:00:04.971
and Employees.

00:00:05.038 --> 00:00:07.540
All Master Agreement Practitioners will benefit from

00:00:07.607 --> 00:00:11.010
knowing when a routine oral counseling session turns into a

00:00:11.077 --> 00:00:15.281
meeting that the Union should attend or into a written counseling.

00:00:15.348 --> 00:00:18.318
Employees will benefit from knowing what to expect if they

00:00:18.385 --> 00:00:21.388
are counseled to improve their performance or conduct.


